<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[preheat oven 180C]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[wash and dry duck pieces. Put in a bag with corn starch and shake to coat. take out and shake off excess]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[heat oil, add sesame oil, deep fry duck 1m then lower heat 5-8m. Do in batches if necessary]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[transfer cooked duck to a baking dish]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[mix the sauce in a bowl with salt and pepper, and pour over the duck]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[bake covererd 30 m, then turn and another 30 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[serve]]></step>
</directions>
